{"tid":1134043,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"克蘇魯題材遊戲《The Sinking City》12分鐘最新實機演示","createTime":"2019-05-01T13:53:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T13:15:44.000Z","uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d445606f603c59b118ec52e320142e6ab612ae14","tid":1134043,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T13:53:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J4z7bkO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ4z7bkO.jpg&h=35453274&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n克蘇魯題材遊戲《The Sinking City》公開了一段12分鐘多的最新實機演示，本作是一款以克蘇魯神話為背景的沙盒開放世界遊戲，玩家將扮演一位身處1920年代的偵探，前往被神秘超自然力量洪水淹沒的馬塞諸塞州新英格蘭小鎮。<br />\n<br />\n遊戲預定將於6月27日登陸PS4/Xbox One/PC，支持中文。<br />\n<br />\nYoutube：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FIbO4Qvd-VM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFIbO4Qvd-VM&d=P2v3VPQ3iBAPr6cjv61qmRAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=b59f7425\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FIbO4Qvd-VM</a><br />\n<br />\nSteam:<br />\n<img src=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/750130/The_Sinking_City/\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F750130%2FThe_Sinking_City%2F&h=b970319e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b07f08b643c9236e2a9fba7a8184ad583cd3f408","tid":1134043,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T13:54:32.000Z","msg":"Steam: <br />\n<a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/750130/The_Sinking_City/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F750130%2FThe_Sinking_City%2F&d=P2v3VPQ3iBAPr6cjv61qmRAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=ebd73db1\" target=\"_blank\">https://store.steampowered.com/app/750130/The_Sinking_City/</a>"},{"pid":"863cdd533b8e1a2117e1ce2f321c4cff30ca55d0","tid":1134043,"uid":194370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T14:26:28.000Z","msg":"第三身克蘇魯個feel幾新鮮"},{"pid":"335539bbc4